Interface TableCell

All Superinterfaces:
org.nasdanika.common.Adaptable, BootstrapElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, HtmlElement, org.nasdanika.ncore.Marked, org.nasdanika.persistence.Marked, org.nasdanika.ncore.ModelElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
TableCellImpl
public interface TableCell extends BootstrapElement
A representation of the model object 'Table Cell'. Table cell - regular or header.

The following features are supported:

  • Header
  • Col Span
  • Row Span
  • Color
  • Background
See Also:
  • BootstrapPackage.getTableCell()
